  "detailed_description": "<h1>Communiy Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dash x Survivors is a roguelite hack n slash bullet hell. Play as Alyssa and overcome increasingly powerful waves of demonic robots.<br><br>Defeating enemies rewards you with a vast selection of <i>Additives</i>.<br>These upgrades not only enhance your character, but also change the look, feel and music during the run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Winning a run unlocks new Additives & permanent upgrades.<br>Death is not the end, as you can spend your earned <i>Components</i> to permanently improve your character.<br><br>Create your very own game-breaking combination!<br>And use it to overcome greater challenges with new enemies, levels and unique bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>DASH</i>. <i>SLASH</i>. <i>DIE</i>. <i>REPEAT</i>.<br><br><br><br><i>(We are a small team of 3 students who work day and night on this game with all our heart because we love roguelikes. We have decided to release Dash x Survivors into Early Access to continue to expand and further develop it to bring you the best we can).</i>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b979f51572b993f22bf27252f143aceb.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dash x Survivors is a roguelite hack n slash bullet hell. Play as Alyssa and overcome increasingly powerful waves of demonic robots.<br><br>Defeating enemies rewards you with a vast selection of <i>Additives</i>.<br>These upgrades not only enhance your character, but also change the look, feel and music during the run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/b8cec8244379b9aea0ab84d524eca36b.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Winning a run unlocks new Additives & permanent upgrades.<br>Death is not the end, as you can spend your earned <i>Components</i> to permanently improve your character.<br><br>Create your very own game-breaking combination!<br>And use it to overcome greater challenges with new enemies, levels and unique bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.poster.avif?t=1715616023\" width=640 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.webm?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2541990/extras/2feba42e9befe06f3111bf08920a5312.mp4?t=1715616023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>DASH</i>. <i>SLASH</i>. <i>DIE</i>. <i>REPEAT</i>.<br><br><br><br><i>(We are a small team of 3 students who work day and night on this game with all our heart because we love roguelikes. We have decided to release Dash x Survivors into Early Access to continue to expand and further develop it to bring you the best we can).</i>",
